Lines.9a5df181-5e19-ec06-701e-b4c2a2effbe9: The balance of the world restored. The balance of many lives, mortal and otherwise, brought to account.
Lines.0020d75f-c235-dc82-201b-926b38b29221: Listen carefully, hero, rebel, friend. I have waited long to tell you these words.
Lines.fce37daa-09fb-48d8-98cd-8c35e91f2942: The balance of the world restored. The balance of these lives, mortal and otherwise, brought to account.
Lines.d3f80e6c-e322-40be-8cc7-4ca564128cbb: Hear me, thou heroes, wastrels, friends. I have waited long to tell you these words.
Lines.7220b339-ba01-4f0c-9a9a-1ce715b9a5d6: Thou played thy part in weaving the fabric of fate itself. But for every thread you sewed, so did the gods unravel another.
Lines.f4e04342-81e6-5d63-9a7d-fd9136560d96: Sleep, rest, revel. But be ready. For thou mayest yet be needed.
Lines.68f0a9e9-3303-4377-0879-2a15e78282c1: Until we meet again, I wish thee every possible fortune. Health, wealth, love, and above all, problems worth solving.
